As a final security measure, Ghosts_Mainframe_Backup (not a node in the extension, only mentioned by Bit) sends a list of incriminating information, some of which is Bit's intentions to leave the Hacknet project and remove PortHack from it. Bit knows this and begins implementing the contingency plan; this then leads to the events of the base game. (done)

